  <title>TEMPORARY ASSISTANT INTERNAL AUDITOR- (12 MONTHS CONTRACT POSITION)</title>
  <link>https://www.ub.bw/connect/job-opportunities/temporary-assistant-internal-auditor-12-months-contract-position</link>
  <description>&lt;span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden"&gt;TEMPORARY ASSISTANT INTERNAL AUDITOR- (12 MONTHS CONTRACT POSITION)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-uid field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden"&gt;&lt;a title="View user profile." href="https://www.ub.bw/user/1558" lang="" about="https://www.ub.bw/user/1558" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" class="username" xml:lang=""&gt;ramahobok&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden"&gt;Tue, 21/02/2023 - 09:12&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;div class="field field--name-field-department field--type-entity-reference field--label-inline clearfix"&gt;
    &lt;div class="field__label"&gt;Department/Faculty&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field__item"&gt;Internal Audit&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;

  &lt;div class="field field--name-field-tender-closing-date field--type-datetime field--label-inline clearfix"&gt;
    &lt;div class="field__label"&gt;Closing Date&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field__item"&gt;Mon, 13 Mar. 2023&lt;/div&gt;
          &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item"&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;UNIVERSITY OF BOTSWANA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;DEPARTMENT OF INTERNAL AUDIT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;VACANCY NO: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;VC/IA01/2023&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;TEMPORARY ASSISTANT INTERNAL AUDITOR- (12 MONTHS CONTRACT POSITION)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The University of Botswana is seeking a Temporary Assistant Internal Auditor to join their team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duties&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;candidate &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;will be responsible for conducting internal audits to assess the effectiveness of the University’s internal controls and procedure. The candidate will also be responsible for identifying areas of risk and providing recommendations for improvement.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Requirements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;: (i) A&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; degree in Accounting, Finance or related field or (ii) part qualified in a professional accounting qualification such as ACCA OR CIMA, (iii) CIA qualification or Association of Accounting Technician qualification is preferred. (iv) post qualification experience in auditing or accounting. (v) the ideal candidate should have strong attention to detail, excellent analytical, and ability to work independently.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;How to apply:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt; Applicants are to address the stated qualification and provide other information to assist the University determine their suitability for the position. They should also quote the vacancy number of the post applied for, provide current CV’s (including telephone, telefax and email), certified copies of educational certificates and transcripts, three reference letters, and send complete documentation to: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Human Resources Manager, Appointments &amp; Administration, Private Bag 0022 Gaborone, Botswana, Telephone: 355 2040/2048/5731, Email: &lt;a href="mailto:ramahobok@ub.ac.bw"&gt;ramahobok@ub.ac.bw&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href="mailto:mfetane@ub.ac.bw"&gt;mfetane@ub.ac.bw&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Applicants should inform their referees to&lt;strong&gt; (i) Quote the vacancy number and position applied for and (ii) submit their references directly to the above address, before the stipulated closing date. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Correspondence will be entered into with shortlisted candidates only&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Hand delivered applications should be submitted to &lt;strong&gt;Office No 108/205. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Closing date: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;13 March 2023&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
